issue.body:
The map does not seem to work. I joined the hackdude group, learned my location here, entered the name as "office==50.8xxxx=4.5xxxx=0" (the x-es are other numbers of course, without quotes). Tapped "track" and checked the map on my location, but nothing.
Also tried with my own group, also nothing.

There's not much to do, so I doubt I'm doing something wrong? 

Nifty tool by the way :)
